{"type":"message","id":"08a652c6","parentId":"45ad4b23","timestamp":"2026-03-19T05:40:32.453Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The context monitor is running and has detected that the context usage is at 66%, which exceeds the 60% threshold. The script is designed to log this but not automatically take action - it's just informing about the status.\n\nAccording to the context-monitor skill, when threshold is reached, it should create a new session. But looking at the script, it just logs a warning. Let me check the skill to see what the expected behavior should be.","thinkingSignature":"e3c4e6452f02cf4c1dec1183948c313664ee98c56ecbb9389c866d7c8d055c8f"},{"type":"text","text":"当前主会话上下文使用情况：\n- **使用率：66%**（131,928 / 200,000 tokens）\n- **状态**：超过 60% 阈值 ⚠️\n\n当前 context 使用较高，建议考虑开启新会话以重置上下文。需要我帮你创建新会话吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1277,"output":156,"cacheRead":37002,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38435,"cost":{"input":0.0003831,"output":0.0001872,"cacheRead":0.00111006,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0016803599999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773898826263}}
